    "comparability_notes": "This is a project-specific EPD for the Hutchinson Builders - Aliro Warehouse project in Brisbane, Queensland. It is produced using GCCA's Industry EPD Tool v4.2. The product is a low-carbon mix (P252080) with a 63% CO2 reduction compared to the simulated baseline. The CO2 reduction baseline is based on Hanson's own simulated baseline using the Green Star Mat-4 Concrete Credit User Guide (2012), not an industry-standard benchmark. EPDs from different programmes or using different PCR versions may not be directly comparable. B1 value is -2.65 kg CO2 eq. representing carbonation (recarbonation) during use stage. Module D value is positive (6.14) which reflects end-of-life scenarios for this product. Reference year is 2023."
